+# Word Garden
+
+> Word Garden is a small TUI game designed as a more cheerful alternative to Hangman. It is intended as a slightly more adventurous "Hello World" project for testing AI-assisted software development. The game includes input validation, state management, a simple loop, win/loss conditions, and a friendly terminal interface.
+
+Word Garden is a friendly terminal word-guessing game. Guess the hidden word before the garden runs out of water. It is like Hangman, but with plants instead of gallows.
+
+## How to Play
+
+Guess one letter at a time. Correct guesses help the plant grow and reveal letters in the hidden word. Wrong guesses cost one unit of water and let weeds appear. Reveal the whole word before the water runs out to win!
+
+### Rules
+
+- Each correct guess reveals all matching letters in the word.
+- Each wrong guess uses one unit of water and grows a weed.
+- Guessing a letter you have already tried does not cost water.
+- Invalid input (numbers, symbols, multiple characters) is rejected and you get another chance.
+- Win by revealing every letter before water reaches zero.
+- Lose when water hits zero with letters still hidden.
+
+## Running the Game
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden
+```
+
+### Options
+
+```bash
+# Choose difficulty (default: normal)
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty easy    # 8 water, 4-6 letter words
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty normal  # 6 water, 5-8 letter words
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard    # 4 water, 7+ letter words
+
+# ASCII-only output (no emoji, for terminals that do not render emoji)
+python3 -m word_garden --ascii
+
+# Combine options
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard --ascii
+```
+
+Press **Ctrl-D** or **Ctrl-C** at any time to quit cleanly.
+
+## Sample Screen
+
+```
+🌿 Word Garden
+
+Word:    G _ R _ E _
+Guessed: A E G R
+Water:  4/6 💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:  2 🌿🌿
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Guess a letter:
+```
+
+### ASCII mode sample
+
+```
+[~] Word Garden
+
+Word:    G _ R _ E _
+Guessed: A E G R
+Water: 4/6 [****]
+Weeds: 2 [--]
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Guess a letter:
+```
+
+## Running Tests
+
+```bash
+python3 -m unittest discover -s tests
+```
+
+## Requirements
+
+- Python 3.11 or newer
+- No external dependencies (standard library only)
